datasets.name: 41e5861b
datasets.query:
with e as (
    SELECT DISTINCT
    account_id, 
    metastore_id, 
    workspace_id, 
    count(entity_id) AS entity_type_count,
    source_table_full_name, 
    source_table_catalog, 
    source_table_schema, 
    source_table_name, 
    source_column_name, 
    source_type, 
    target_table_full_name,
    target_table_catalog, 
    target_table_schema, 
    target_table_name,
    concat_ws('', source_table_catalog, source_table_schema) s_cat_schema,
    concat_ws('', target_table_catalog, target_table_schema) t_cat_schema,
    collect_set(target_column_name) target_column_name,
    size(collect_set(target_column_name)) number_col_derived,
    target_type, 
    count(event_date) total_events,
    MAX(event_date) AS max_event_date 
    FROM system.access.column_lineage 
    --- where 
    -- source_table_catalog like 'oagflightstats%'
    -- where (source_table_catalog like 'oagflightstats%' or source_table_catalog like 'qar_v1_dev_azr_%') 
    where target_table_catalog <> source_table_catalog
    and year(event_date) = 2025
GROUP BY
    account_id, 
    metastore_id, 
    workspace_id, 
    source_table_full_name, 
    source_table_catalog, 
    source_table_schema, 
    source_table_name, 
    source_type, 
    target_table_full_name, 
    target_table_catalog, 
    target_table_schema, 
    target_table_name,
    target_type,
    source_column_name
ORDER BY total_events DESC
),
f as (
    select *, element_at(array('CAD','CAE','PLM','BOM','AHM','CBM'), cast(floor(rand() * 6) + 1 as int)) AS domain from (
    select distinct source_table_catalog, source_table_schema from system.access.table_lineage)
)

select e.*, f.domain from e join f on e.source_table_catalog  = f.source_table_catalog and e.source_table_schema = f.source_table_schema

datasets.name: 276ffce9
datasets.query:
with e as (SELECT DISTINCT
    account_id, metastore_id, workspace_id, entity_type, count(entity_id) AS entity_type_count,
    source_table_full_name, source_table_catalog, source_table_schema, source_table_name,
    count(source_path) AS source_path_count, SPLIT_PART(source_path, '/', 3) AS s3_bucket_name, source_type, target_table_full_name,
    target_table_catalog, target_table_schema, target_table_name, target_path, target_type, created_by,
    MAX(event_date) AS max_event_date
FROM system.access.table_lineage
GROUP BY
    account_id, metastore_id, workspace_id, entity_type,
    source_table_full_name, source_table_catalog, source_table_schema, source_table_name,
    SPLIT_PART(source_path, '/', 3), source_type, target_table_full_name, target_table_catalog, target_table_schema, target_table_name,
    target_path, target_type, created_by
ORDER BY max_event_date DESC
),
f as (
    select *, element_at(array('CAD','CAE','PLM','BOM','AHM','CBM'), cast(floor(rand() * 6) + 1 as int)) AS domain from (
    select distinct source_table_catalog, source_table_schema from system.access.table_lineage)
)

select e.*, f.domain from e join f on e.source_table_catalog  = f.source_table_catalog and e.source_table_schema = f.source_table_schema

SELECT DISTINCT account_id, metastore_id, workspace_id, source_table_catalog , target_table_catalog 
FROM system.access.table_lineage
where source_table_catalog is NOT NULL
